  "title": "History teacher",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver lessons in an engaging and dynamic manner, based on our curriculum and pedagogy</li>\n  <li>Develop lesson materials and provide feedback to help students achieve visible improvement in academic results</li>\n  <li>Engage students and help them realize their potential</li>\n  <li>Teach Secondary Geography, History and Social Science Subjects</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree obtained from Singapore Local Government Universities</li>\n  <li>Strong in Humanity Subjects</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate passion in education – committed to nurturing the students and makes effort to continually improve yourself</li>\n  <li>Dynamic and confident, with an approachable disposition</li>\n  <li>Strong communication (both spoken and written) and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Required to work on weekends</li>\n  <li>Candidates with prior teaching experience are preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
